      <data key="d52">False</data>
      <data key="d53">Manual findings plus S29 show ATPL_00304 is a real mixed corridor whose weighted reparameterization is ineffective but whose transfer-equivalent strengthening materially reduces its loading; future treatment should prioritize parallel/transfer-equivalent handling.</data>
